    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "text",
        "responseBody": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Vector Scouter — Cancelar Inscrição</title>\n<style>\n  body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#0a0a0a; font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; min-height:100vh; }\n  .box { text-align:center; padding:48px; max-width:400px; }\n  .icon { font-size:48px; margin-bottom:24px; }\n  h1 { font-family:Georgia,serif; font-size:28px; font-style:italic; color:#f0f0f0; margin:0 0 12px; }\n  p { font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.7; margin:0; font-weight:300; }\n  .badge { display:inline-block; background:rgba(0,206,209,0.1); color:#00CED1; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:3px; margin-bottom:24px; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"box\">\n    <div class=\"icon\">✓</div>\n    <div class=\"badge\">Vector Scouter</div>\n    <h1>Inscrição cancelada</h1>\n    <p>Você não receberá mais o relatório semanal de IA. Se mudar de ideia, basta se cadastrar novamente no site.</p>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
